name: By the Mystical São Francisco
description:
The photo was captured on 35mm film by the river São Francisco in Alagoas' state. The man with the guitar is a traveler street-musician named Wanlenyo and during this shot, he was smoothly playing for the mother nature and spirits that live there. This image was also a short-film cover recorded in a magic and mystical area called Sertão located in Brazil's northeast.
